/**
 * Setup Instructions:
 *
 * 1. Google Analytics 4:
 *    - Create GA4 property: https://analytics.google.com/
 *    - Get Measurement ID and API Secret
 *    - Add to .env.local:
 *      GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
 *      GA4_API_SECRET=your_api_secret
